Name: Frequency of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' compared to the total number of declarations processed.
Metric: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' out of all cases where '' does not happen

Name: Percentage of declarations leading to 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' out of all declarations rejected for any reason.
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'count': "activity == 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'", 'metric_condition': '> 0', 'aggregation': 'percentage', 'filter': "activity LIKE 'Declaration REJECTED by %'"}

Name: Number of times 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' occurs directly after 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'.
Metric: Number of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' activities for cases where activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' occurs

Name: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' followed by a resubmission of the declaration ('Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE').
Metric: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' out of all 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Frequency of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' in relation to the total number of 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'.
Metric: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' out of all 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' out of all declarations that were not approved by any of the approval steps (ADMINISTRATION, BUDGET OWNER, PRE_APPROVER, SUPERVISOR).
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'count': "activity == 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'", 'metric_condition': '> 0', 'aggregation': 'percentage', 'filter': "activity LIKE 'Declaration APPROVED by %'"}

Name: Number of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' occurrences per month to identify patterns or trends over time.
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'count': "activity == 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'", 'aggregation': 'total', 'group_by': 'month'}

Name: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' that occur in declarations with amounts above 100 euros.
Metric: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' out of all cases

Name: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' in the total declarations processed by the SYSTEM compared to those processed by STAFF MEMBER.
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'count': "activity == 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'", 'metric_condition': '> 0', 'aggregation': 'percentage', 'filter': "org:resource == 'SYSTEM' OR org:resource == 'STAFF MEMBER'"}

Name: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' in declarations that required director approval, to see if higher-level scrutiny impacts rejection rates.
Metric: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' out of all cases

Name: Frequency of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' before and after 'Request Payment' to understand if rejections happen more before or after payment requests.
Metric: Number of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' activities for cases where activity 'Request Payment' occurs

Name: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' for domestic trips compared to international trips, based on the description that domestic trips require no prior permission.
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'count': "activity == 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'", 'metric_condition': '> 0', 'aggregation': 'percentage', 'filter': "case:description LIKE '%domestic%' OR case:description LIKE '%international%'"}

Name: Number of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' that are eventually approved after being resubmitted, to measure the effectiveness of the resubmission process.
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'count': "activity == 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'", 'aggregation': 'total', 'filter': "activity == 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' AND activity == 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'"}
